# Business Card App 

## App Name: Business Me
   
## App Description 

**Description:** Our app allows users to **create the image** they want to convey to **potential business partners** and **possible investors** alike!!  

### General App Attributes 

**Category:** Design App 

**Mobile:** Easy to make Business cards and add variety to them as well. A Business Contact app in your pocket It's offline. Bump function audio dings.

**Story:** To leave an impression on new contacts and inviting them into your network. Whether it be on a resume or a business card we strive to make your name stand out.

**Market:** Our app has potential in everyone's lives, but our top market consists of men and women in the age range between 20-35 who want to market themselves or their company.

**Habit:** Any time you meet a potential business acquaintance you want to leave a good impression.

**Scope:** 
* Minimum Viable Product: Bump function. Create business cards and resumes. 
* Product: Design own template. Can use your custom template 
* Premium: Pre-made templates. Can't use your custom template.
* WE NEED LAWYERS!!!
